dct_title_s: Map of the Island of Bombay
dct_description_sm: India. [Bombay Housing Panel]. Companion text: The Greater Bombay scheme. Report of the Housing Panel. January 1946. Bombay: [Housing Panel.] 1946. 104 p. 2 folded maps (in end pocket.]. Handwritten on verso: "from the Greater Bombay Scheme. Rept. of the Housing Panel. Jan 1946." Map Library does not have the accompanying report.
